      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence studies were performed on the pedicle screw and rod construct geometry. Peak stress and construct stiffness quantities of interest showed less than 2% change on final mesh refinement, confirming discretization error is controlled."
