      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity replicates the ASTM F1717 test configuration used as the regulatory acceptance benchmark. The validation domain closely matches the intended simulation use, supporting the credibility of model predictions for the submission context."
