    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted by the assessment team given the regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 as the standard acceptance test and the absence of alternative loading conditions in the applicable standard. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
